title: Ankara pencil dress
descriptions: An Ankara pencil dress is a stylish and form-fitting garment made from vibrant and distinct African wax print fabric known as Ankara. These dresses are typically knee-length and feature the eye-catching and bold Ankara patterns, making them a fashionable choice for both casual and formal occasions.

title: Silk Boubou Dress
descriptions: Indulge in the timeless allure of the Silk African Bubu Dress, marrying luxurious silk with traditional African design for an effortlessly chic statement piece that transcends borders and captivates with its grace and sophistication.

title: Mary Set
descriptions: This is a classic and elegant two piece set made for the modern corporate woman.

title: Two-Piece suit
descriptions: Elevate your style with our African Two-Piece Set, blending contemporary fashion with traditional African prints. Crafted for versatility and flair, each piece embodies the vibrancy and culture of Africa, offering a modern twist on timeless elegance.

title: Bella Set
descriptions: Classic corporate ladies ready to wear two piece with an African touch.

title: Eswathi Shirt
descriptions: Stand out with this vibrant red and black African shirt! Made with comfort and style in mind, this unique piece is perfect for any occasion.

title: African Shirt
descriptions: Embrace timeless elegance with our red and white African shirt. The crisp white fabric is adorned with striking red patterns, offering a sophisticated twist on traditional African design. Made for comfort and confidence, this shirt is perfect for adding a touch of cultural flair to your everyday wardrobe.
